Summary: Glowing white round/solid object moving 40 mph across the treeline.
divs: Sighting DetailsTook my dog outside to do his business when I got home from work and witnessed an odd round glowing object shoot over the treeline going n to s. it appeared to have some small wing structure that circled the entire object. It looked like nothing I have ever seen before. I lost sight of the object as it disappeared in the trees. I am very confused as to what it was. this is the third UFO sighting here at Valley of the Moon I have witnessed in the past year.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Kenwood
